---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import missionImage from '../assets/images/about-mission-image.png';
import '../styles/about-mission.css';
---

<section class="about-mission">
  <div class="container about-mission__container">
    <div class="about-mission__visual">
      <Image src={missionImage} alt="Perfume bottle in warm light" class="about-mission__image" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
    </div>

    <div class="about-mission__content">
      <p class="about-mission__label">Our Mission</p>
      <h2 class="about-mission__title">Our Olfactory Universe</h2>
      <p class="about-mission__lead">
        Fragrance is an art form that touches science, history, and psychology. We cover the full spectrum, ensuring no stone is left unturned.
      </p>

      <div class="about-mission__list">
        <div class="about-mission__item">
          <span class="about-mission__dot" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" class="about-mission__dot-icon">
              <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="8" />
              <path d="M6 10.3l2.2 2.2L14 6.9" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <p><strong>History & Developments:</strong> We dig deep into the archives to explore the origins of legendary houses and iconic moments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-mission__item">
          <span class="about-mission__dot" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" class="about-mission__dot-icon">
              <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="8" />
              <path d="M6 10.3l2.2 2.2L14 6.9" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <p><strong>The Science of Notes:</strong> We break down aroma anatomy and explain how notes interact from top to base.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-mission__item">
          <span class="about-mission__dot" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" class="about-mission__dot-icon">
              <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="8" />
              <path d="M6 10.3l2.2 2.2L14 6.9" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <p><strong>Designers & Houses:</strong> Behind every bottle is a visionary and we spotlight both iconic and rising creators.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-mission__item">
          <span class="about-mission__dot" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" class="about-mission__dot-icon">
              <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="8" />
              <path d="M6 10.3l2.2 2.2L14 6.9" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <p><strong>Trends & The Inside View:</strong> We decode market shifts and ingredient movements with practical perspective.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-mission__item">
          <span class="about-mission__dot" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" class="about-mission__dot-icon">
              <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="8" />
              <path d="M6 10.3l2.2 2.2L14 6.9" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <p><strong>Education For Every Level:</strong> From beginner scent guides to advanced note breakdowns, we create content that helps every reader grow.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-mission__item">
          <span class="about-mission__dot" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" class="about-mission__dot-icon">
              <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="8" />
              <path d="M6 10.3l2.2 2.2L14 6.9" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <p><strong>Global Perspective:</strong> We track fragrance culture across regions so you can discover how perfumery evolves around the world.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-mission__item">
          <span class="about-mission__dot" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" class="about-mission__dot-icon">
              <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="8" />
              <path d="M6 10.3l2.2 2.2L14 6.9" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <p><strong>Practical Buying Clarity:</strong> We compare concentration, longevity, projection, and style so you can choose scents with confidence.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
